name: Numeric Fiddle Thinkpiece© series : Timepeace
description:
Numeric Fiddle Thinkpiece© series : Waitlessness
At first I wanted to call this series "Numeric Graphite Thinkpiece", but what the hell are NGTs even? So graphite became fiddle. Fiddle is synonym for doodle. NFT. Done.

As far as thinkpiece goes, it's quite the opposite. This is the kind of stuff that comes out when I let myself draw aimlessly. This is us, struggling to handle time, like the hare in Alice in Wonderland. 
Enjoy!
